  "commentary": "With SPX at 6849.77 sitting just below the massive +8044.2M gamma wall at 6850, dealers are positioned to aggressively sell any push higher as they're long gamma and need to hedge by selling rallies. The PIN regime with 61.3B in total GEX creates a strong gravitational pull toward the 6837-6850 zone, with dealers providing stabilizing flow against momentum moves. Key resistance comes from the stacked positive gamma walls at 6850/6875/6900, while any break below the GEX flip at 6837 would shift dealers into buying mode.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to get pinned around 6850 with limited upside as dealers sell strength.",
